  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Extinct VR, an immersive single-player action-adventure and exploration VR experience that transports you to a bizarre realm filled with strange occurrences and challenging obstacles. In Extinct VR, you step into the shoes of an ordinary man thrust into extraordinary circumstances, navigating through a captivating universe where every corner hides new mysteries.                 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter unique life forms reminiscent of cyborgs remnants of an advanced civilization that has faced its downfall. As you delve deeper into this enigmatic world, you’ll face a series of puzzles and formidable foes, each with their own tactics and weaknesses.       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the freedom of movement with both free locomotion and teleportation mechanics, allowing you to explore your surroundings and interact with the environment in unprecedented ways. Extinct VR also has a mode with a seated play feature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join us on this thrilling journey where courage, wit, and resourcefulness are your greatest allies. Will you uncover the secrets of Extinct VR and survive its many trials?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to the world of Extinct VR, an immersive single-player action-adventure and exploration VR experience that transports you to a bizarre realm filled with strange occurrences and challenging obstacles. In Extinct VR, you step into the shoes of an ordinary man thrust into extraordinary circumstances, navigating through a captivating universe where every corner hides new mysteries.                 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/9b06d5658024e9dc23d8421fe91d8e56.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Encounter unique life forms reminiscent of cyborgs remnants of an advanced civilization that has faced its downfall. As you delve deeper into this enigmatic world, you’ll face a series of puzzles and formidable foes, each with their own tactics and weaknesses.       </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/fa58ebdff6f67e5fedda41403803e358.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/d632596582d90a9254e92fa0765c57b7.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the freedom of movement with both free locomotion and teleportation mechanics, allowing you to explore your surroundings and interact with the environment in unprecedented ways. Extinct VR also has a mode with a seated play feature.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.poster.avif?t=1739206964\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.webm?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3179710/extras/86de235e6cd0689b14f5ec935ba3524b.mp4?t=1739206964\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Join us on this thrilling journey where courage, wit, and resourcefulness are your greatest allies. Will you uncover the secrets of Extinct VR and survive its many trials?</p>",
